      <title>优衣库母公司瞄准强劲的西方市场，力争提高销售额</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uniqlo-owner-s-earnings-beat-eyes-bigger-sales-in-fiscal-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迅销株式会社 (Fast Retailing Co.) 在向西方新市场扩张的过程中帮助这家日本服装店运营商抵消了中国市场经济放缓的影响，因此该公司计划在 2025 财年实现更高的销售额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-10/uniqlo-owner-s-earnings-beat-eyes-bigger-sales-in-fiscal-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:13:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
